answers.body_markdown:
`glBindTexture` takes the texture **target** not the **unit**.

Targets are: GL_TEXTURE_1D, GL_TEXTURE_2D, GL_TEXTURE_3D, GL_TEXTURE_CUBE_MAP, GL_TEXTURE_1D_ARRAY, GL_TEXTURE_2D_ARRAY (and extension specific targets).

The texture *unit* is passed to `glActiveTexture` and these are GL_TEXTURE0, GL_TEXTURE1 and so on, and is also what the sampler uniform is set to.

---

Change your code to

        glActiveTexture(GL_TEXTURE0);
    --- glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, textures[0]);
    +++ glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, textures[0]);

and

        glActiveTexture(GL_TEXTURE1);
    --- glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, textures[1]);
    +++ glBindTexture(GL_TEXTURE_2D, textures[1]);

